edu.ucsc.cross.hse.core.modeling

Class HybridSystem<X extends DataStructure>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucsc.cross.hse.core.modeling.HybridSystem<X>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HybridDynamics<X>

    public abstract class HybridSystem<X extends DataStructure>
extends java.lang.Object
implements HybridDynamics<X>
    The base class for implementing hybrid system models. This class is extended to create a new class that defines a hybrid system of the form defined in the user manual. An extension requires the state class and dynamics to be defined through the hybrid dynamics interface. Intended Operator: User
